name: Scooby and the GAN, Part 2: The Haunted Forest
description:
Scooby is all alone in The Haunted Forest and he’s not quite feeling like himself. Maybe he shouldn’t have eaten those mushrooms he found in the pasture, but he was all out of Scooby Snacks.
